---
import LegalLayout from '../../../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Data Sources"
  description="Public data sources used by PatientBillGuide — CMS MPFS, NCCI, and hospital price files."
  pageClass="page-data-sources"
  hideTitle
  crumbs={[
    { label: 'Methodology', href: '/methodology/' },
    { label: 'Data Sources' },
  ]}
>
  <section class="guide-hero guide-hero--data" slot="hero" aria-labelledby="data-hero-title">
    <div class="guide-hero__bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="guide-hero__orb guide-hero__orb--1"></span>
      <span class="guide-hero__orb guide-hero__orb--2"></span>
      <span class="guide-hero__grid"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="container guide-hero__inner">
      <p class="guide-hero__eyebrow">Methodology · Public data</p>
      <h1 id="data-hero-title" class="guide-hero__title">Data Sources</h1>
      <p class="guide-hero__lead">
        Every benchmark on PatientBillGuide traces back to government-published files — not secret insurer
        databases or crowdsourced guesses.
      </p>
      <div class="data-pipeline" aria-label="Data flow from CMS to your browser">
        <div class="data-pipeline__node">
          <span class="data-pipeline__badge">CMS</span>
          <span>MPFS · NCCI</span>
        </div>
        <span class="data-pipeline__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        <div class="data-pipeline__node">
          <span class="data-pipeline__badge">Build</span>
          <span>gzip JSON bundle</span>
        </div>
        <span class="data-pipeline__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        <div class="data-pipeline__node">
          <span class="data-pipeline__badge">CDN</span>
          <span>static /data/</span>
        </div>
        <span class="data-pipeline__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        <div class="data-pipeline__node data-pipeline__node--you">
          <span class="data-pipeline__badge">You</span>
          <span>browser lookup</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="data-source-cards">
    <article class="data-source-cards__card data-source-cards__card--mpfs">
      <h2>CMS Medicare Physician Fee Schedule (MPFS)</h2>
      <p class="data-source-cards__role">Primary price anchor</p>
      <p>
        Primary source for Medicare allowed amounts by CPT/HCPCS code and geographic locality. Published by
        the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services (CMS). Updated annually (and sometimes quarterly
        for some files).
      </p>
      <p>
        Used by: <a href="/tools/fair-price/">Fair Price Calculator</a>,
        <a href="/tools/bill-auditor/">Bill Auditor</a>,
        <a href="/tools/hospital-compare/">Hospital Price Compare</a>,
        <a href="/codes/">CPT encyclopedia</a> cost context.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="data-source-cards__card data-source-cards__card--ncci">
      <h2>NCCI edits</h2>
      <p class="data-source-cards__role">Coding integrity signals</p>
      <p>
        National Correct Coding Initiative (NCCI) procedure-to-procedure edits help identify code pairs that
        Medicare typically does not pay separately when billed together. We use these as <em>possible</em>
        unbundling signals — not proof of error. See
        <a href="/methodology/billing-flags/">billing flags methodology</a>.
      </p>
      <p>Used by: <a href="/tools/bill-auditor/">Bill Auditor</a>.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="data-source-cards__card data-source-cards__card--hospital">
      <h2>Hospital price transparency &amp; care-setting estimates</h2>
      <p class="data-source-cards__role">Facility vs office context</p>
      <p>
        Hospitals publish machine-readable standard charges under federal transparency rules. Our
        <a href="/tools/hospital-compare/">Hospital Price Compare</a> tool combines MPFS physician fees with
        documented facility multipliers by care setting (office, ASC, hospital outpatient, ER) — so you can
        see why the same CPT code costs more at a hospital department than an independent clinic.
      </p>
      <p>
        Direct ingestion of every hospital chargemaster file is on the roadmap; current facility estimates
        use published CMS context and curated setting benchmarks. See
        <a href="/methodology/limitations/">limitations</a>.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="data-source-cards__card data-source-cards__card--zip">
      <h2>ZIP-to-locality mapping</h2>
      <p class="data-source-cards__role">Geographic accuracy</p>
      <p>
        Medicare pays different amounts in different localities. We map your ZIP code to the correct MPFS
        locality using CMS geographic crosswalk files so benchmarks reflect your area — not a national
        average.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <h2>What we do not use</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Proprietary insurer negotiated rate databases</li>
    <li>AMA-licensed CPT code descriptions (we write original plain-English summaries)</li>
    <li>User-submitted bill data to train models — tools run client-side</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Update cadence</h2>
  <p>
    Data bundle versions and last-updated dates are shown in each tool's interface and in
    <code>/data/manifest.json</code> on the live site. Methodology pages are updated when we ship new CMS
    releases — typically following the annual MPFS final rule.
  </p>
  <p>
    Related: <a href="/methodology/price-benchmarks/">Price benchmarks</a> ·
    <a href="/methodology/limitations/">Limitations</a> ·
    <a href="/privacy/">Privacy policy</a>
  </p>

  <section class="guide-cta guide-cta--data" aria-label="Explore methodology">
    <h2>See how we use this data</h2>
    <div class="guide-cta__grid">
      <a href="/methodology/price-benchmarks/" class="guide-cta__card">
        <strong>Price benchmarks</strong>
        <span>Fair range math explained</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/methodology/billing-flags/" class="guide-cta__card">
        <strong>Billing flags</strong>
        <span>Confidence levels &amp; NCCI</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/tools/fair-price/" class="guide-cta__card">
        <strong>Fair Price Calculator</strong>
        <span>Live MPFS lookup</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</LegalLayout>

<style is:global>
  .page-data-sources .legal-page__body {
    --guide-accent: #059669;
    --guide-accent-bg: #ecfdf5;
    --guide-accent-border: #6ee7b7;
  }

  .guide-hero--data {
    --hero-accent: #10b981;
    --hero-accent-light: #34d399;
    --hero-bg: linear-gradient(165deg, #022c22 0%, #065f46 42%, #047857 100%);
  }

  .data-pipeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem 0.25rem;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: rgb(0 0 0 / 0.25);
    border: 1px solid rgb(52 211 153 / 0.3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .data-pipeline__node {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.85);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .data-pipeline__badge {
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    background: rgb(16 185 129 / 0.25);
    border: 1px solid rgb(52 211 153 / 0.5);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #6ee7b7;
  }

  .data-pipeline__node--you .data-pipeline__badge {
    background: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.15);
    border-color: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.4);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .data-pipeline__arrow {
    color: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.45);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .data-source-cards {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .data-source-cards__card {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.04);
    border-left-width: 4px;
  }

  .data-source-cards__card--mpfs { border-left-color: #059669; }
  .data-source-cards__card--ncci { border-left-color: #0d9488; }
  .data-source-cards__card--hospital { border-left-color: #6366f1; }
  .data-source-cards__card--zip { border-left-color: #0891b2; }

  .data-source-cards__card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .data-source-cards__role {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: #059669;
  }

  .data-source-cards__card--ncci .data-source-cards__role { color: #0d9488; }
  .data-source-cards__card--hospital .data-source-cards__role { color: #6366f1; }
  .data-source-cards__card--zip .data-source-cards__role { color: #0891b2; }

  .data-source-cards__card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .guide-cta--data {
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ecfdf5 0%, #d1fae5 100%);
    border: 1px solid #6ee7b7;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  }

  .guide-cta--data h2 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
    color: #047857;
  }

  .page-data-sources .guide-cta__card {
    border-color: #a7f3d0;
  }

  .page-data-sources .guide-cta__card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgb(5 150 105 / 0.15);
  }

  .page-data-sources .guide-cta__card strong {
    color: #047857;
  }
</style>
